"zručnosťami."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:67
#, kde-format
msgid "Yi 1.5 is a high-performing, bilingual language model."
msgstr "Yi 1.5 je vysoko výkonný dvojjazyčný jazykový model."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:68
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Command R is a Large Language Model optimized for conversational interaction "
"and long context tasks."
msgstr ""
"Command R je veľký jazykový model optimalizovaný pre konverzačnú interakciu "
"a úlohy s dlhým kontextom."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:69
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A general-purpose model ranging from 3 billion parameters to 70 billion, "
"suitable for entry-level hardware."
msgstr ""
"Univerzálny model v rozsahu od 3 miliárd do 70 miliárd parametrov, vhodný "
"pre základný hardvér."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:70
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A LLaVA model fine-tuned from Llama 3 Instruct with better scores in several "
"benchmarks."
msgstr ""
"Model LLaVA doladený z Llama 3 Instruct s lepšími skóre v niekoľkých "
"benchmarkoch."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:71
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Zephyr is a series of fine-tuned versions of the Mistral and Mixtral models "
"that are trained to act as helpful assistants."
msgstr ""
"Zephyr je séria doladených verzií modelov Mistral a Mixtral, ktoré sú "
"trénované na fungovanie ako nápomocní asistenti."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:72
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A lightweight AI model with 3.8 billion parameters with performance "
"overtaking similarly and larger sized models."
msgstr ""
"Ľahký model AI s 3,8 miliardami parametrov s výkonom prekonávajúcim podobne "
"veľké aj väčšie modely."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:73
#, kde-format
msgid "Embedding models on very large sentence level datasets."
msgstr "Modely vkladania na veľmi veľkých dátových sadách na úrovni viet."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:74
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Codestral is Mistral AI’s first-ever code model designed for code generation "
