msgstr ""
"Codestral je vôbec prvý kódový model Mistral AI navrhnutý pre úlohy "
"generovania kódu."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:75
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"StarCoder is a code generation model trained on 80+ programming languages."
msgstr ""
"StarCoder je model na generovanie kódu trénovaný na viac ako 80 "
"programovacích jazykoch."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:76
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"General use chat model based on Llama and Llama 2 with 2K to 16K context "
