#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:80
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Wizard Vicuna Uncensored is a 7B, 13B, and 30B parameter model based on "
"Llama 2 uncensored by Eric Hartford."
msgstr ""
"Wizard Vicuna Uncensored je model s 7B, 13B a 30B parametrami založený na "
"Llama 2 necenzurovaný Ericom Hartfordom."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:81
#, kde-format
