msgid ""
"A fine-tuned model based on Mistral with good coverage of domain and "
"language."
msgstr "Doladený model založený na Mistral s dobrým pokrytím domény a jazyka."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:116
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A model from NVIDIA based on Llama 3 that excels at conversational question "
"answering (QA) and retrieval-augmented generation (RAG)."
msgstr ""
"Model od NVIDIA založený na Llama 3, ktorý vyniká v konverzačnom zodpovedaní "
