#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:117
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Conversational model based on Llama 2 that performs competitively on various "
"benchmarks."
msgstr ""
"Konverzačný model založený na Llama 2, ktorý súťažne dosahuje výsledky v "
"rôznych benchmarkoch."

#: plugins/ollamacommon/ollamacommonmodelutils.cpp:118
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"SQLCoder is a code completion model fined-tuned on StarCoder for SQL "
